{"tid":2314843,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紅線下的記者｜國安法下傳媒進入冰封時代 立場記者昇哥︰新聞自由已經好脆弱","createTime":"2020-12-06T20:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T08:29:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd43503fef3d150420ee4c8a751aef3cf7389685","tid":2314843,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T20:46:19.000Z","msg":"「你說修改通例，一定是不合理，坦白說。修改通例都算，你利用 GMNIS （政府新聞處系統）一刀切，更加不合理。GMNIS 只是一個新聞平台，當中只有80多間是本地傳媒，好像有80多間傳媒，甚至不是本地媒體，例如《四川日報》。整件事是很不合邏輯。」胡戩說。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_768978_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_768978_0&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2tUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=37a6d682\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_768978_0&h=b6671347\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_768978_0</a>"},{"pid":"37a72e91ea45fb015058ad9c42473b47f9803b54","tid":2314843,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T20:57:08.000Z","msg":"邊個影相我就拉邊個"},{"pid":"feb7efac391b2c57dd5a8798def3b70a0c6deef8","tid":2314843,"uid":214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T21:55:39.000Z","msg":"上年拉晒入封鎖線再噴椒已經知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363e26305377b5e8b2482914f92155571d30e0e7","tid":2314843,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:23:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5847fc0b79038e468972ce13002593a449ed6838","tid":2314843,"uid":138964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"記者呢一刻變哂戰地記者啦<br />\n<br />\n冇人身保障 軍政底冇權利<br />\n<br />\n一係就做情報搜集賣料<br />\n戰時情報員無誤"},{"pid":"7c6eb4bc71b982fab6d9acf4517868fa0e0e1def","tid":2314843,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}